<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361624" n="1"/>
   <opener><lb/>Viro <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> et <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>.
                           <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs>.
                           <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus Antonius Michelotti</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
   <p><lb/>Quin Tibi gratuler, <subst><del>Vir</del><add>A</add></subst>micissime Vir, propterea quod a <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr>
                           <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patruele</rs> Tuo certior factus sum de <add>Tuo</add> Matrimonio,<note type="comment">1720-06-03 Erste Heirat mit Anna Maria Birr (1681-1747), Tochter des Melchior Birr, Spezierer, und der Margarethe geb. Wettstein.</note><del>Tuo</del> sane
                              <lb/>facere non possum: pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quum intelligam Te, uxo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem multum admodum divitem duxisse. De hac igitur re vehe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>menter l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tor. Ceterum quid agas; an rebus mathematicis
                              <lb/>des operam; an aliqu<subst><del>am</del><add>od</add></subst> pereximium opus mathematic<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>(de quo s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>pius Te rogavi) editurus sis, scire cupio. Id non
                              <lb/>modo ego, sed <add>et</add> Amplissimi nostri Mecenates, quibuscum de
                              <lb/>Te <add>crebram facio</add> commemorationem, optant. Nostram itaque expec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tationem ne frustreris etiam atque etiam oro.</p>
   <p> <lb/>Meam <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_M3G2JA79">Dissertationem</rs> propediem editurus sum uti etiam
      <lb/>aureas Inclyti <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> Tui mihi semper suspiciendi Disser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tationes.</p>
<p> <lb/>Sub fin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> <date when="1720-08">Augusti</date> spero rem fore ad umbilic<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> deductum,
   <lb/>quo tempore <subst><del>an</del><add>simne</add></subst> in <rs type="place" key="place_VER-frankr">Gallias</rs><del> sim</del> profecturus,<del><gap/></del> Te certio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rem faci<subst><del>o</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></add></subst>. Quod si non erit, uti credo, rogabo <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs>
   <lb/>ut quamprimum mittat <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Fili<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> istuc commorant<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>,
                              <lb/>cui <add>polliceor omne officium me<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></add> in rebus medicis, et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim in Medicina facienda<del>inser-</del>
                              <lb/><del>viam</del>, <subst><del>et</del><add>uti etiam</add></subst> in omnibus, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad ejus utilitatem, et glori<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> spec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tent.</p>
   <p> <lb/>In Annotationibus istius<del> F</del> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">ejusd<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> Filii, Patruelis Tui</rs>, ad <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_8VCJJVI7">Tenta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>men V de Motu Musculor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-124275087">Jacobi Keillii</rs>, rem video, de
                              <lb/>qua an <add>absolute</add> vera sit, jure dubito. Nonne videmus, inquit, mercuri<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>cutem membran<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> crass<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> penetrare, quum id<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> non valeat epidermi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dem membran<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> tenuissim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> pertransire. Quid? Nonne mercurii
                              <pb facs="1361626" n="2"/>
<lb/>particul<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vel Pinguedini porcin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> permist<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, et epidermid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>,
                              <lb/>et cut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> penetrant in iis, quibus utpote Lue venerea conflic<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tatis, Inunctio mercurialis ad Salivation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> excitandam
                              <lb/>adhibetur? Id quotidiana docet experientia. Non enim mercu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rii globuli, cut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> penetrare <add>possunt,</add> nisi prius epidermid<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> subje<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rint.</p>
   <p> <lb/>Vell<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> habere <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_DM34UH9S">Dissertation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> de Usu Matheseos in Medicina</rs>
                           <lb/>a <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120379260"><abbr>Jo.</abbr> Jacobo Scheuchzero</rs> composita, istuc vero edita <abbr>An.</abbr>
                                                      <lb/><date>1701</date> in 4. Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea mihi gratissima essent Doctissimi <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Verens<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>feldii</rs> Vestri Scripta omnia.<note type="internal">ToDo: Eventuell auf UB-Katalog verweisen.</note> Si ejusmodi scripta ad me
                              <lb/>mittes, pergrat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> facies, uti si et mihi indicabis quanti stent.
   <lb/>Pecuni<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> enim <abbr>Clariss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117589144">Patrueli</rs> hic optima cum valetudine
                              <lb/>commoranti confestim redd<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>. Quod reliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> est, ut Illustrissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> salutem plurimam meo nomine dicas vehe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>menter opto; velimque<del> ut Tibi persuadeas</del> sic existimes,
                              <lb/>Te mihi nihil gratius facere posse quam si intellexero,
                              <lb/><add><del>me a Te</del></add>et Te bene valere, et me a Te plurimum diligi.</p> <closer>Fac igitur
                                 <lb/>ut valeas,<add>meque amare pergas.</add> Dabam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1720-07-05">Tertio Nonas Julii 1720</date>.</closer>
<postscript><p><lb/><abbr>P. S.</abbr> </p>
   <p><lb/>Rogo, ut cum aliis, quos mittes libros, ad me transmitt<subst><del>es</del><add>ere cures</add></subst> ill<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-120597519"><abbr>Jo.</abbr> Gronin<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gii</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_D9K78QUC"><subst><del>i</del><add>H</add></subst>istoriam Cycloidis</rs>, in <add>qua</add> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118639749">Hugenii</rs> <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_5QXNJKBI">Annotata Posthuma</rs> in <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_6CP8LL78"><abbr>libr.</abbr> <abbr>Phil.</abbr>
         <lb/><abbr>Nat.</abbr> <abbr>Princ.</abbr> Mathematica</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544"><add><abbr>Is.</abbr></add> Newtoni</rs> contineri, me certiorem fecit
      <lb/>Eruditissimus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> Tuus.</p></postscript>
</div>
